et nutrients from foods that include avacados apples oranges banannas as part of their construction this year i employed a new technique something i learned from last year when i went to grab my whole grain almond butter avocado sandwich on my bike – it had turned to mush – as well as the bag of whole foods sweet potatoes – but i just squeezed the bag and i ate it like space man food it was yummy and my body liked it and it was easier to consumer in mash form so that is what i do real food mush bagsin the end be creative but try to stay clean with your eating eating clean is your bodies best friend when it comes to hydration and nutrition during exercise also experiment with different levels of intake before during and after exercise use the weeks leading up to the race to will help you find the right hydration and nutrition strategy for your body filed under triathlete triathlon jon sabes hydration  notes october   tips for proper running technique jon sabes is a highly experienced executive in the financial industry with more than  years of service he has worked with a variety of businesses in developing their financing capabilities apart from his professional pursuits jon sabes is an avid swimmer biker and runner who enjoys endurance athletics long distance runners should focus on their form in order to improve their running speed and avoid injury two major considerations in proper runner’s form are the arms position and torso activation the arms should be only swing forward and back in a motion that is parallel with the body and with the elbows bent at a degree angle many runners mistakenly swim their arms side to side across their torso which increases stress on the spine and does not add to the forward momentum of running when the forearms become tense or fists begin to clench runners should drop them to the side and shake them out to release all tension try focusing on your fingers  pinching them together to create a tension which you can direct your focus towards the head and shoulders influence the position of the torso when the head is up and the shoulders are low and loose with the back straight the runner’s torso position will promote optimal oxygen intake the lungs will then be free to expand to full capacity a slight lean forward allows gravity to work in your favor helping propel you forward through the air try focusing on your tail bone  allowing it to slide back and tucking it under to feel the change in your hip positionproper running technique will ensure maximum performance with minimal injury to the body when you run see how long you can focus on aspects of form alone  holding your concentration on form can improve your running and pass the time quickly as the miles go by filed under jon sabes financial industry runners gwg holdings inc gwghoq people  reuterscom x edition united states africa américa latina عربي argentina brasil canada  deutschland españa france india italia  méxico россия united kingdom united states gwg holdings inc gwghoq related topics stocksstock screenermarket datafinancialslife  health insurance overview news key developments people charts financials analysts research pulse gwghoq on nasdaq stock exchange capital market usd pm edt change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  summary name age since current position jon sabes   chairman of the board chief executive officer william acheson   chief financial officer steven sabes   executive vice president  originations and servicing secretary director chris orestis  executive vice president  life insurance secondary markets david abramson   independent director shawn gensch   independent director charles maguire   independent director jeffrey mcgregor   independent director mark schwarzmann   independent director dan callahan  director  communication » insider trading biographies name description jon sabes mr jon r sabes serves as chairman of the board chief executive officer of the company he i